<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>&quot;CARRIED BYTHE ANGELS&quot;</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal In hawih lopitak kawtkhak bul achun,
 Pathien cha khat thi dingin a um;
 Khawvel limsak loh, bangmah neilopa kha,
 Ngaiin, vanah danglam nan a ngak.

[V2]
 Angelte'n chawlhna gamah a pui to ui,
 Thil gihawih vana gitna ah;
 Hukdampa'n A na lawp, van ankuong um di'n,
 Ngaih cheng tawh Paradis-ah a um.

[V3]
 2. Damsung buoina hun tawp chuh bang ahi dem?
 Zie thu hi dawtin I um sek ui;
 Khawvel lam hak a hin puokgik I puou ui,
 Lungkham mitthi luonna gam ahin.

[V4]
 3. Isu zui, khawvel ah hau lo mahleh chin,
 Go mantam in van ah a hun ngak;
 Patepna na tuok cheng kipahna'n ngaiin,
 Kithenna chuh hung tung pai ta'n a.

[V5]
 4. Masuon zelin chieh in Lalpa a dingin,
 Na phat leh talent Amah di'n pie'n;
 Nasep tawm mahleh, na kipahman tam ding,
 Zie'n Kross-vanah kipahna lukhuk.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>398</hymn_number>
</song>